{"tid":2282891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★公屋輪候時間5.6年 較上一季上升0.1年","createTime":"2020-11-12T07:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T10:47:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b63948df3052bc41d9450df5c12e4404a3391576","tid":2282891,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:18:34.000Z","msg":"房屋委員會今(12日)公布最新公屋輪候冊數字，在2020年9月底，約有15.64萬宗一般公屋申請，及約10.36萬宗配額及計分制下的非長者一人申請，輪候冊合共達26萬宗申請。一般申請者的平均輪候時間為5.6年，當中長者一人申請者的平均輪候時間為3.3年。<br />\n<br />\n上述兩者的平均輪候時間較上一季，即2020年6月底，分別上升0.1年及0.3年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201112/bkn-20201112135526651-1112_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201112%2Fbkn-20201112135526651-1112_00822_001.html&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2AuyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=6d6a62cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201112/bkn-20201112135526651-1112_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c7da52a50d6f6ffc7ce724864b9fe35aeaa4c278","tid":2282891,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:19:17.000Z","msg":"全民公屋not a dream<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b4476faba5aca8aa6f86dd766530d19ec3cea1","tid":2282891,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jZOR4b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jZOR4b.gif&h=94dab9c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2785658/neighbor_thumb_20201024_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2